vertices u, v with distance d
shortcut e = (u, v) with length d

delete v, add shortcuts maintain to maintain shortest-path info
neighbors u, w so that u -> v -> w is shortest path u -> w
                       and no alt shortest path excluding v
              (a 'witness' proves we dont need a shortcut. alt)
  add shortcut (u, w) with cost |u->v| + |v->w|

preprocessing:
  - order vertices
  - remove vertices until one remains
